<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Auroville Community</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .sidebar .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .sidebar-button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background-color: #34495e;
            color: #ecf0f1;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .main-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f1ece6;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card-image {
            width: 150px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .card-content {
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #e67e22;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://aurovillenetwork.org/uploads/default/original/1X/99e32f00cb6f0520758dd2efd953b3628be0efe3.png" alt="Auroville Community Logo">
        </div>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/u/lucas/activity" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-dashboard"></i> Dashboard</a>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/c/announcements/5" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-announcement"></i> Announcements</a>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/c/events/13" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-event"></i> Events</a>
        <a href="https://aurovillenetwork.org/categories" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-forum"></i> Categories</a>
        <a href="#" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-social"></i> Social</a>
        <a href="https://directory.auroville.services/" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-directory"></i> Directory</a>
        <a href="#" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-references"></i> References</a>
        <a href="#" class="sidebar-button"><i class="icon-help"></i> Help Center</a>
    </div>
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="calendar-icon.png" alt="Calendar" class="card-image">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Events Calendar</h2>
                <p>Auroville has a lot going on. It's not always easy to follow. Thanks to our calendar, you can make sure you won't miss the events which speak to you.</p>
                <button class="button">View all events</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="forum-icon.png" alt="Forum" class="card-image">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Community Forums</h2>
                <p>Auroville is a collective adventure. Discussing respectfully among ourselves is healthy - and we have designed a platform to facilitate this.</p>
                <button class="button">Join the discussion</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
